GENSHIN ROSTER
==============

Your full Genshin Impact character roster — element filters, sort, artifact
detail on click. Runs as a static web app via a Cloudflare Worker proxy.


FIRST-TIME SETUP
----------------

Step 1 — Deploy the Cloudflare Worker (one time only):

     cd worker
     npm install
     npx wrangler login        ← opens browser to authenticate
     npx wrangler deploy       ← prints your Worker URL when done

     The URL looks like: https://genshin-roster.your-name.workers.dev
     Copy it for the next step.

Step 2 — Open the app:

     python server.py          ← opens http://localhost:5001

     Or just open index.html directly in your browser.

Step 3 — Fill in the setup form (one time, saved to localStorage):

     Worker URL   → the URL from Step 1
     ltuid_v2     → from hoyolab.com cookies (see below)
     ltoken_v2    → from hoyolab.com cookies (see below)
     UID          → your in-game UID (pause menu, bottom right)


GETTING YOUR HOYOLAB COOKIES
-----------------------------

  1. Go to https://www.hoyolab.com and log in.
  2. Open DevTools (F12) → Application tab → Cookies → https://www.hoyolab.com
  3. Copy the values for ltuid_v2 and ltoken_v2.

Cookies expire after a few weeks. When they do, you'll see an error in the
app — just refresh the cookies via ⚙ Settings and paste the new values.


REFRESHING DATA
---------------

Roster data is cached for 5 minutes. Hit the ↺ button to force a fresh fetch.


CLI MODE (optional)
-------------------

If you prefer a terminal table instead of the web UI:

     pip install -r requirements.txt
     cp config.example.json config.json   ← fill in cookies + UID
     python roster.py
